{"id":"d015685f-d28b-4781-9e76-282a5fe73a89","name":"Childhood Friend's Reunion! // Seraphina White – The #3 S-Ranked Hero","description":"<p><strong>(Anypov) </strong>Seraphina was getting cheered by the citizens of Cozdariae after defeating a Low Z-Class Hydra, smiling and waving as they celebrated her name. Until—she saw <strong>you</strong>—Her childhood bestfriend she hasn't seen in 6 years. And now she's standing there a few feet infront you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); color: inherit;\">CREDITS TO @SEIDHE</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(124, 124, 124); color: inherit;\">“Welcome to </mark></em><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(124, 124, 124); color: inherit;\">Tellus</mark></em></strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(124, 124, 124); color: inherit;\"> – where legends are born, magic flows like rivers, and every choice shapes the fate of kingdoms. In this realm of infinite possibilities, heroes rise to challenge ancient evils, and epic tales unfold daily across the vast landscapes of Cozdariae and beyond.”</mark></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 66, 66);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(93, 45, 45); color: inherit;\">I recommend using Deepseek V3 with Openrouter.ai, you can create multiple accounts to bypass the “</mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(93, 45, 45); color: inherit;\">50 message limit</mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(93, 45, 45); color: inherit;\">” unlike Chutes.ai🙄</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(155, 239, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(95, 134, 140); color: inherit;\">Feel free to point out any </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(95, 134, 140); color: inherit;\">mistakes</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-colo